{"tid":687473,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"金正恩「反引力梯形頭」反映性格固執","createTime":"2018-06-02T09:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T09:33:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3649e9201602c3479170e335f427a5e95a05ae07","tid":687473,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:41:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180602/20408731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180602%2F20408731&d=xD%2BGrjRUql2tyaiMwagBQbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=c29c2b35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180602%2F20408731&h=7f001d46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180602/20408731</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月02日 <br />\n<br />\n金正恩「反引力梯形頭」反映性格固執<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180602/large/02wx03p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180602%2Flarge%2F02wx03p.jpg&h=54c6e59d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■金正恩髮型獨特。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n北韓領導人金正恩在美韓峯會前頻頻現身，側面和後腦經常出鏡，令其獨特髮型再引起熱議，有髮型師更從中看穿其缺點，指金正恩性格固執。<br />\n<br />\n這個被美國《紐約時報》形容為「違反地心引力的梯形頭」，髮型師稱為「slick back undercut」，據有54年經驗的南韓理髮師池德容說明，將兩側與後側剃掉，再將頭頂長髮「誇張的」向後吹整。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又被稱為「法西斯髮型」<br />\n<br />\n美國國際理髮師協會曾上載圖解，教人「4步剪出金正恩頭」，第一步是以刨剃掉兩側，用剪髮器修剪髮根，頂部留1.5吋長頭髮往後梳，最後用髮蠟定型；但另一名南韓理髮師指出，金正恩用的是髮型噴霧，再用吹風機吹整，「即使會讓臉看起來比較大，他依然堅持留這種髮型，看來個性極端且固執」，但好處是毋須仔細分層與整理。<br />\n<br />\n據傳，1920年代英國黑幫及1930至40年代的德國納粹黨員間也流行這髮型，因此又稱「法西斯髮型」、「希特勒青年頭」。<br />\n<br />\n南韓《朝鮮日報》  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n兩韓將開會談離散家庭團聚<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n沙地公主《Vogue》影開車照被轟粉飾政權<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩韓將開會談離散家庭團聚<br />\n<br />\n北韓特使到訪白宮金正恩親筆信稱欲見特朗普"},{"pid":"da5840c907a3132733dfe5e44eb6bc56123e94ce","tid":687473,"uid":39316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T10:33:54.000Z","msg":"家族髮型黎架喎"},{"pid":"08470a44aea140e5df23d09c3db2bd43d033618c","tid":687473,"uid":131690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T10:49:47.000Z","msg":"個樣兇狠啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97caeb3ab01c6f49ef7d9f35b9aa074bdd57f829","tid":687473,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da5840c907a3132733dfe5e44eb6bc56123e94ce","tid":687473,"uid":39316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T10:33:54.000Z","msg":"家族髮型黎架喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T09:33:31.000Z","msg":"反映全家性格固執,OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}